        <p>Every program I made was fulfilling because I knew it was me who built it from scratch. I designed and created a dynamic web application called Bridge, using Ruby on Rails, HTML, and CSS. Bridge is a platform designed to connect clients directly to freelancers, inspired by the increasing unemployment in South Africa. Take a look at it! <font color="blue"><u>(www.bridgeconnect.co)</u></font></p><br/>
